<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1"&gt;12S1 Sagāthāvaggasaṃyuttapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/2"&gt;2 Devaputtasaṃyutta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/12S1/2/2.2"&gt;2.2 Anāthapiṇḍikavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;2.2.10 Anāthapiṇḍikasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Devaputtasaṃyutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Anāthapiṇḍikavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Anāthapiṇḍikasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_462"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;101.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;462&lt;/span&gt;Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_463"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;463&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;isisaṃghanisevitaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;pītisañjananaṃ mama.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_464"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;464&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Kammaṃ vijjā ca dhammo ca,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sīlaṃ jīvitamuttamaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Etena maccā sujjhanti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;na gottena dhanena vā.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_465"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;465&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Tasmā hi paṇḍito poso,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sampassaṃ atthamattano;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;evaṃ tattha visujjhati.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_466"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;466&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Sāriputtova paññāya,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sīlena upasamena ca;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yopi pāraṅgato bhikkhu,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;etāvaparamo siyā”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_467"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;467&lt;/span&gt;Idamavoca anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto. Idaṃ vatvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyi. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_468"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;468&lt;/span&gt;Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi—  “imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññataro devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho, bhikkhave, so devaputto mama santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_469"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;469&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;‘Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;isisaṃghanisevitaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;pītisañjananaṃ mama.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_470"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;470&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Kammaṃ vijjā ca dhammo ca,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sīlaṃ jīvitamuttamaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Etena maccā sujjhanti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;na gottena dhanena vā.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_471"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;471&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Tasmā hi paṇḍito poso,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sampassaṃ atthamattano;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;evaṃ tattha visujjhati.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_472"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;472&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Sāriputtova paññāya,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sīlena upasamena ca;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yopi pāraṅgato bhikkhu,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;etāvaparamo siyā’ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_473"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;473&lt;/span&gt;Idamavoca, bhikkhave, so devaputto. Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyī”ti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_474"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;474&lt;/span&gt;Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca—  “so hi nūna, bhante, anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhavissati. Anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati āyasmante sāriputte abhippasanno ahosī”ti. “Sādhu sādhu, ānanda, yāvatakaṃ kho, ānanda, takkāya pattabbaṃ anuppattaṃ taṃ tayā. Anāthapiṇḍiko hi so, ānanda, devaputto”ti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_12S1_475"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;475&lt;/span&gt;Anāthapiṇḍikavaggo dutiyo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="SUMMARY" id="p_12S1_476"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;476&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="firstLetter"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;assuddānaṃ&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_12S1_477"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;477&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Candimaso ca veṇḍu ca,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Dīghalaṭṭhi ca nandano;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Candano vāsudatto ca,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Subrahmā kakudhena ca;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Uttaro navamo vutto,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Dasamo anāthapiṇḍikoti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="273714" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 2.2.9 Uttarasutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="272696" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="272697" title="Go to next page"&gt;2.3 Nānātitthiyavagga &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
